76561198347966442,Recommended,486780,29511304,Posted: 26 January,all,aharshvive,"Tons of fun and the accuracy is great. You can stab fruit, slice individually from any direction, do combos for more points, and smack bombs aside with the side of the blade. Great game to show people who won't be into shooters or scary heights games. There's don't let any fruit fall mode, score as much as possible without hitting bombs mode, and just score as much as possible mode, but my favorite is survival mode. All the other modes deal mostly with horizontal cuts, but in survival mode canons launch fruit at you so your cuts are usually going away from you rather than side to side. It really makes a difference slashing away and I like how that switches it up."
